name: Data Entry (StatsCloud Beta)
description: StatsCloud, Data Entry.  A hands on tutorial covering the basics of data entry using the StatsCloud statistical app. The StatsCloud site (https://statscloud.app/) is a full statistics package (similar to SPSS, Jamovi, and JASP).  View this tutorial and others at https://sites.google.com/view/p2l/statscloud-data-entry-beta-version.
